            "content_html": "<ul>\n<li>Editor: Phur Tsham [普仓, Pǔcāng]</li>\n<li>Title: Ratnāvalī: Critical Edition of the Sanskrit Manuscript from Xizang [梵文写本《宝鬘论颂》校勘与研究]</li>\n<li>Place: Lhasa</li>\n<li>Publisher: Tibet Tibetan Ancient Books Publishing House [西藏藏文古籍出版社]</li>\n<li>Year: 2024</li>\n<li>Series: Palm-Leaf Scripture Special Text Excavation Series [贝叶经特殊文本专项挖掘系列丛书]</li>\n<li>Series Part: 3</li>\n</ul>\n"
