        {
            "type": "field",
            "label": "Extent",
            "inline_text": null,
            "content_html": "<ul>\n<li>The complete work is extant.</li>\n<li>The edition contains a complete text.</li>\n<li>The text consist of 504 verses, 503 of which are normal two-line anuṣṭubh.</li>\n<li>The text is spread out over 223 pages in the edition, interspersed with verse-by-verse Chinese and Tibetan collation, plus many footnotes.</li>\n</ul>\n"
